<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<h2 id="preparing-for-a-no-deal-eu-exit-5-key-areas-businesses-must-be-aware-of">Preparing for a no deal EU Exit: 5 key areas businesses must be aware of</h2>

<p>Watch an hour long video about 5 key areas UK businesses must be aware of to keep trading with the EU if the UK leaves without a deal.</p>

<p>The video covers:</p>

<ul>
  <li>applying for an <abbr title="Economic Operator Registration and Identification">EORI</abbr> number</li>
  <li>transitional simplified procedures</li>
  <li>preparing to make customs declarations</li>
  <li>entry summary declarations (also known as safety and security declarations)</li>
  <li>paying the correct import and export duty, and VAT</li>
</ul>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZnsLMsjCQZI&list=PL8EcnheDt1zjoo7bz6y_HJBFtPMTkkvDl&index=2&t=3s">Preparing for a no deal EU Exit: what businesses need to be aware of</a></p>

<h2 id="importing-goods">Importing goods</h2>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZnsLMsjCQZI&list=PL8EcnheDt1zjoo7bz6y_HJBFtPMTkkvDl">Importing goods from the EU to the UK in a no deal EU Exit in 10 steps</a></p>

<h2 id="exporting-goods">Exporting goods</h2>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lgi0XKJRp3I&feature=youtu.be">Exporting goods from the UK to the EU in a no deal EU Exit in 10 steps</a></p>

